# @VERSION spec:gdla v:0.1.0 generated:2026-04-04 source:api-agent
# Project Atlas — Atlas Finance API v2.1 (mid-build evolution)

@D atlas-finance-api|Atlas finance API mid-build snapshot|2.1.0|https://api.acme.internal/finance/v2

@AUTH bearer|JWT bearer issued by Acme SSO|Authorization
@AUTH service_token|mTLS service-to-service token|x-service-token

@S JournalEntry|Mid-build journal entry — added validation envelope
 entryId|string|required|uuid|Primary key
 postingDate|string|required|date|Effective accounting date
 accountId|string|required|uuid|GeneralLedger account ID
 amount|number|required||Posted amount
 amountBase|number|||Base-currency translation
 fxRate|number|||FX rate snapshot
 sourceKind|string|required||Origin classification
 sourceEventId|string||uuid|Upstream event identifier
 postedBy|string|required||Acting principal
 postedAt|string|required|date-time|Server-side timestamp
 reversesEntryId|string||uuid|Reversal pointer
 batchId|string||uuid|Batch identifier
 version|integer|required||Increments on supersession
 validationOk|boolean|required||Set after validator runs (mid-build addition)

@S ValidationError|New schema for explicit validator failures
 code|string|required||Validation error code (e.g. ZERO_AMOUNT, ACCOUNT_CLOSED)
 message|string|required||Human-readable message
 entryId|string||uuid|Affected entry, if any

@S GeneralLedger|Modernised account
 accountId|string|required|uuid|Primary key
 accountCode|string|required||Chart of accounts code
 accountName|string|required||Display name
 status|string|required||Lifecycle status
 currency|string|required||ISO currency
 openedAt|string|required|date-time|Opening date

@EP GET /accounts|Lists active accounts|listAccounts
@EP POST /accounts|Creates a new account|createAccount
@EP GET /accounts/{id}|Returns a single account|getAccount
@EP PATCH /accounts/{id}|Updates an account|patchAccount
@EP GET /journal|Lists journal entries with filters|listJournalEntries
@EP POST /journal|Posts a new manual journal entry|createJournalEntry
@EP POST /journal/batch|Bulk posts journal entries (added Apr 4)|createJournalEntriesBatch
@EP POST /journal/{id}/reverse|Reverses an entry|reverseJournalEntry
@EP GET /journal/{id}/audit|Returns audit trail|getJournalAuditTrail

@R JournalEntry -> GeneralLedger|references
@R ValidationError -> JournalEntry|references|ValidationError refers to the rejected entry
